panel.title: Multiple Mimiga Mask
panel.field: Based on ZarroTsu's NPC patches for <MIM, this hack allows for more than one type of Mimiga Mask hack to be in use, thanks to Noxid utilizing the original hack within <VAR.
You have the option to hook the 3 Quote NPCs (111, 112, and 150) to whichever variable you see fit, allowing up to 4 <MIM hacks to be used simultaneously.
This hack requires usage of separate bitmaps in order for this to work. Recommend bitmaps include PIXEL.bmp, CREDIT01.bmp, Loading.bmp, and StageImage.bmp.
This hack is a supplement to the TSC+ and TSC+ Improved hacks! It's only compatible with the 16x16 version of <VAR0006 so far, 16x17 version coming soon!
- Bitmap assignment can be changed through npc.tbl, you can access it through the Entity map editor in Booster's Lab.
- Always be sure to have a documentation of your variables, so you can remember which one has the <MIM function.
- Use <VAR0006:YYYY (or any of the variables chosen) in order to use the hack.

field.name: Restore all Quote NPCs to use <VAR0006. (Apply this first time if Noxid's version of TSC+ is being used!)
